                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <h2>Multi-Authentication</h2>
                            <p>Implement secure authentication with multiple providers including JWT, Google, and GitHub OAuth strategies all in one unified system.</p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="card">
                            <div class="card-icon">
                                <svg width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
